This paper discusses reducing energy cost in data centers, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also proposes a scheduling algorithm to optimize workload and reduce energy cost, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and performance analysis (cs.PF). The paper also mentions request routing, which is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
